# Cargo.lock IS tracked here. This workspace is not a bare library: it builds
# firmware images that get flashed to real hardware, and tulle tracked its own
# lockfile for exactly that reason before the 2026-07-23 radio merge. Losing it
# in the merge is how a fresh resolution picked `fixed` 1.31.0 (rustc >= 1.93)
# and broke the t114 build on an older default toolchain.

